{
  "stem": "9446.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and the war, after the war, 1945, May, there was an agreement between Russian and Polish, the new Polish government, you know, that the former Polish citizens, Poles or Jews, if they want to return to Poland, they can do so.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we already-- we immediately, sign up on that list, you know, and hoping that we will find some survivors in Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Ha.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We came to Poland [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in '46.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "No, before going to Poland, yes, [INAUDIBLE], before going to Poland we went to Austria.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because that's where they sent  us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We  only could go wherever they sent us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were in a little town called Linz in Austria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there we got a hold of a rabbi, and a whole group of us got like a common wedding, whatever you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they gave us rings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then we were-- I still have the [NON-ENGLISH] Do you know what that is?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Do you know what that is?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I still have it somewhere here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And a rabbi officiated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were married in accordance with the Jewish law.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, we were trained by some people, by some Jewish organization, to become halutzim in Israel-- Palestine at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, we were considering the possibility of going to-- to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, nothing materialized, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't go there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- what happened then?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We talking about-- oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, of course, we were sent-- there was an organization, UNRRA, United Nations Refugee something organization, which was kind of in charge of all the refugees.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were refugees, you know, victims of the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they send us to Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
